data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and spacious living in this 3 bedroom, 4 bathroom home located on a corner lot.     From the moment you step inside, you'll be welcomed by an open floorplan. This home boasts multiple living areas, ensuring plenty of space for relaxation, entertainment, and everyday life.    One of the major highlights of this property is its strategic location. Military installations are just minutes away, making your daily commute a breeze. And for those who enjoy retail therapy, shopping is also conveniently close, meaning you can easily indulge in your favorite stores.    This home is more than a place to live; it's a hub for your lifestyle. Whether you're drawn to its proximity to military installations, shopping, or simply the comfort of a well-designed home, this property has it all. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the harmonious blend of convenience, comfort, and an ideal location that this home offers. Your dream lifestyle awaits!
